graphql.query:
query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	oAuthGetCredentials (query: $query)
	{
		id
		grantType
		username
		password
		accessTokenId
		refreshToken
		clientSecret
		redirect
	}
}

query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	oAuthFindCredential (query: $query)
	{
		id
		grantType
		username
		password
		accessTokenId
		refreshToken
		clientSecret
		redirect
	}
}

query ($id:ID)
{
	oAuthFindCredentialById (id:$id)
	{
		id
		grantType
		username
		password
		accessTokenId
		refreshToken
		clientSecret
		redirect
	}
}

mutation ($payload:OAuthUpdateCredentialInput!)
{
	oAuthUpdateCredential (payload:$payload)
	{
		id
		grantType
		username
		password
		accessTokenId
		refreshToken
		clientSecret
		redirect
	}
}

mutation ($id:ID!)
{
	oAuthDeleteCredentialById (id:$id)
	{
		id
		grantType
		username
		password
		accessTokenId
		refreshToken
		clientSecret
		redirect
	}
}

mutation ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	oAuthDeleteCredentials (query: $query)
	{
		id
		grantType
		username
		password
		accessTokenId
		refreshToken
		clientSecret
		redirect
	}
}
